ZH: 乃是一直以来的好朋友。
EN: You have always been a good friend.

ZH: 乃可直接联系我。
EN: You can contact me directly.

ZH: 乃不用担心，我会替你解决。
EN: You don't have to worry, I will take care of it for you.

ZH: 乃之前就知道这个消息。
EN: You already knew about this news.

ZH: 乃有令人印象深刻的能力。
EN: You have an impressive ability.

ZH: 乃会永远留在我们的心中。
EN: You will always stay in our hearts.

ZH: 乃一直以来都对我很支持。
EN: You have always been very supportive of me.

ZH: 乃怎么会这么容易相信他？
EN: How could you believe him so easily?

ZH: 乃不是轻易相信别人的人。
EN: You are not someone who easily believes in others.

ZH: 乃有勇气面对困难。
EN: You have the courage to face difficulties.

ZH: 乃对每个人都很友善。
EN: You are very friendly to everyone.

